dct_title_s: Travel map of Taiwan : central Taiwan / Tourism Bureau.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading. Map shows county boundaries, six classes of roads; railroads; national parks, scenic, and forest areas; tourist information. Ancillary map on recto:Taichung City. Scale 1:13,800. Tourist information, color illustration and maps on verso, including national parks and national scenic areas. On verso: Shei-Pa National Park -- Tri-Mountain National Scenic Area -- Lisha -- Tri-Mountain National Scenic Area --Mt. Bagua -- Sun Moon Lake National Scenic Area. "Jan. 2011 printed." On cover: "TAIPEI INTL FLORA EXPO 2010/11/06-2011/04/25".
dct_creator_sm: China (Republic : 1949- ). Jiao tong bu. Guan guang ju.
dct_publisher_sm: Tai bei shi, Taiwan : Tourism Bureau, 2011.
